edBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚多黑警藍絲共匪想唔失敗都幾難"},{"pid":"a2a616d7ac03fd63015323e9c1eef99eb3291c93","tid":1871149,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"而家先知？"},{"pid":"720a9fe4dbd1d876e72c8540cfd374d746a6a44c","tid":1871149,"uid":346958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T15:59:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>新一輪口罩統計上線啦</em></strong><br />\n今次統計埋過去五日嘅口罩供應<br />\n越多人做估算越準！<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/2QdDrU3WH4YubuZw6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F2QdDrU3WH4YubuZw6&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqjrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=de984e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/2QdDrU3WH4YubuZw6</a><br />\n一分鐘唔洗做完！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[學術] 之前問大家啲口罩捱到幾耐，係時候再問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1871378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1871378</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>2月3號嘅結果</em></strong><br />\n之前問大家啲口罩捱到幾耐，入嚟睇結果 [多圖]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1864594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1864594</a>"}]}